create table Deletes(
     delete_id int auto_increment,
    version_number int not null ,
     file_id int not null,
     delete_date date not null,
     primary key(delete_id,version_number,file_id),
     foreign key(version_number)references File_version (version_number)on delete cascade on update cascade,
     foreign key(file_id) references File (file_id) on delete cascade on update cascade,
